ISLAMABAD, Feb 19 (APP):Minister for Energy Hammad Azhar on Saturday said high level economic growth every year has not only increased income of the people but also help creating millions of jobs.
The power generation and consumption in Pakistan has been increasing by 9 per cent annually, he said in a tweet. “This indicates 5 per cent increase in economic growth this year as well,” he said.
